    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD hemolysis model for the CPB COU based on satisfactory performance across the 10 assessed credibility factors, all of which met or exceeded required levels at MRL 3. Three factors (use error, test samples, equivalency of input parameters) were not assessed but were considered beyond the scope of the current submission and not material to the primary hemolysis index QoI. The output comparison results, discretization error analysis, and model form justification collectively provide sufficient evidence to support the regulatory submission decision.",
